    {
      "n": 35,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee irr Bââlam Aug- ftimus darrifschi/ kas irr eekſch Ben-Innoma Eeleijas/ ka tee fa- wus Dehlus/un fawas Meitas Molokam zaur Uggunti likſchti eet/ fo es teem ne efmu paweh- lejs/ nedś manirr Sirdi nahzis/ ka teem bij ſcho Negantibu dar- riht/ ka tee Juhdu darrifcu greh- kojam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 36,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un nu/ tapehz fakka tas KUNGS/ tas Israêta Deews ta no ta Pilsfahta / no ka juhs fakkat : Tas irr tam Rehnixam no Babeles Rohkā dohts zaur Sobinn/ un zaur Baddiu/ un zaur Mehri.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 37,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Rangi/ Es fapulzinaſchu tohs no wiſahm Semnehim/ korp es tohs efmu dsinits eekſch mannas Dufmibas / un eekſch mannas Bahrsibas/ un eekſch mannas leelas Apſaikchanas/ un atweddichu tohs atkaz uhs fcho Weetu/ un likſchu tohs bes Bibjaschanas dſihwoht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 38,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee buhs man par Laudin/ un es buhschu teem par Deewu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 39,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un es dohschu teem wee- nadu Sirdi/ un weenadu Zeffu/ ka tee mannis bihſtabs wiſu fa- wn Mahschu/ par winno pafchu Labbum/ lihds ar winnu Behr- neem pehz winneem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 40,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un es darrifschu ar teem weenu muhschigu Derribu / ka es no winneem ne grtbbu at- kahpt/ ka es teem labba darriu/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 35,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "un es dohschu fawu Bibjascha- uu winneem Sirdi/ ka tee no mannim ne atkahpj.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 41,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un es preezafschofs pahr teem/ winneem labba darriht/ un es dehſtifchu tohs fchai Seim- mê peetizzigi/ no wiſas mannas Sirde/ un no wiſas mannas Dwehfeleg.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 42,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo ta fakka tas KUNGS: Itt ka es pahr scheem Laudin esnuu weddis wiſu ſcho leeſu Lau- numu/ta weddichu es pahr teem wiſu Labbu/ fo es pahr teem runnaju.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 43,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Tibruni taps pirktf fchai Seimmē/ no ka juhs fak- kat: Ta irr pohtā/ ka neweens Jilweks/ nedś Lohps tur irratd/ ta irr teem Kaldeereem Rohkā dohta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 44,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tibruni taps par Nan- du pirkti/ un Grahmatas raksti- tas/ un aissebgeletas/ un Leezt- neekt to apleezinahs eekſch Ben- jamina Seimes/ un apfahrt Jeruſalemes gullamahm Wee- tahm/ un eekſch teem Pilsfah- teein Juhda/ un eekſch to Kalnu Pilsfahteem/un eekſch to Eeleiju Pilsfabteem / un eekſch teem Pilsfahteem prett Deenas-Wid- dus Puft/ jo es nogreecischu winno Zeetunu / fakka tas KUNGS.\n"
    }
  ],
